That&#39;s wonderful, Frank! I hope they are wrong on that, but they could be right. The clock is ticking, and I guess we&#39;ll know soon enough.

As for annoying people and nay-sayers as far as the boxes are concerned, I&#39;ve learned just not to read posts by those people. That way I don&#39;t allow them to make me upset. If people want to learn about this field, that&#39;s one thing. But if they want to trash it, and trash those of us trying to establish communication with unseen beings, I just don&#39;t even read their posts anymore. 

~Draiga


